## 1. Compute

| Function | AWS | Azure | GCP |
|----------|-----|-------|-----|
| Virtual machines | EC2 | Virtual Machines (VM) | Compute Engine (GCE) |
| Auto-scaling | Auto Scaling Groups (ASG) | Virtual Machine Scale Sets (VMSS) | Managed Instance Groups (MIG) |
| Serverless functions | Lambda | Azure Functions | Cloud Functions |
| PaaS / app hosting | Elastic Beanstalk | App Service | App Engine |
| Batch processing | AWS Batch | Azure Batch | Cloud Batch |
| Bare metal | EC2 Bare Metal | Bare Metal Servers | Bare Metal Solution |

---

## 2. Containers & Kubernetes

| Function | AWS | Azure | GCP |
|----------|-----|-------|-----|
| Managed Kubernetes | EKS | AKS | GKE |
| Container orchestration (proprietary) | ECS | Container Instances (ACI) | Cloud Run (serverless containers) |
| Serverless containers | Fargate | Container Apps | Cloud Run |
| Container registry | ECR | Azure Container Registry (ACR) | Artifact Registry / Container Registry (GCR) |

