## 3. Storage

| Function | AWS | Azure | GCP |
|----------|-----|-------|-----|
| Object storage | S3 | Blob Storage | Cloud Storage (GCS) |
| Block storage | EBS | Managed Disks | Persistent Disk |
| File storage | EFS / FSx | Azure Files | Filestore |
| Archive / cold storage | S3 Glacier | Blob Archive tier | Cloud Storage Archive |

