| NoSQL (key-value/document) | DynamoDB | Cosmos DB | Firestore / Bigtable |
| In-memory cache | ElastiCache | Azure Cache for Redis | Memorystore |
| Data warehouse | Redshift | Synapse Analytics | BigQuery |

