---

> **Quick takeaway:** The most-used DevOps trio in daily work tends to be **compute** (EC2 / VM / GCE) + **managed Kubernetes** (EKS / AKS / GKE) + the **monitoring stack** (CloudWatch / Azure Monitor / Cloud Monitoring), wired together with **Terraform** for cross-cloud IaC.